    {
        "content": "<p>Aha, <code>type_context_old::is_def_eq_args</code> unifies explicit arguments or implicit arguments of the form <code>t =?= ?m</code> first, before doing implicits. But the problem <code> @continuous_linear_map real real real.semiring real.semiring ‚Ä¶ =?= @continuous_linear_map ?m_1 ‚Ä¶</code> looks like its first argument should be of that form <span aria-label=\"thinking\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f914\" role=\"img\" title=\"thinking\">:thinking:</span></p>",
        "id": 269376429,
